Amelia Okoli-Okpalaoka (14 Mee 1941 1 Nọvemba 2017) bụ nwanyị na-eme egwuregwu n'egwuregwu na Naijirịa
Ọ bụ ọkachamara na ihe omume ịwụli elu n'oge ọrụ ya
Okoli nọchitere anya Naijiria na 1964 Olympic Games
O kwuru na o nwetara ihe nrite ọla edo maka mba ya dị n'Ebe Ọdịda Anyanwụ Afrịka na 1965 All-Africa Games
Okoli mechara nke iri na 1958 British Empire na Commonwealth Games high jump.
Àtụ:Footer All-Africa Champions High Jump Women
